English | July 15, 2005 | ISBN: 0804836507 | 149 Pages | PDF | 20 MB


Take your paper folding to an advanced level with this user-friendly origami book.
From shimmering hummingbirds to magnificent bats, from a stunning panther mask to graceful sea turtles, Michael G. Lafosse's complex and beautiful origami projects are well known around the world.
